[I] A powerful network analysis framework

[T] Zeek is a powerful network analysis framework that is much different from
[T] the typical IDS you may know.

[U] https://www.zeek.org

[A] Vern Paxson
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] base/system

[E] opt nodejs

[L] BSD
[V] 8.2.1

[D] deb14d87687e9b10b2c28b8d64bde798b158348290551f6ea671557a zeek-8.2.1.tar.gz https://github.com/zeek/zeek/releases/download/v8.2.1/

var_remove_regex confopt ' ' '--bindir=.*'
var_remove_regex confopt ' ' '--sbindir=.*'
var_remove_regex confopt ' ' '--datadir=.*'
var_remove_regex confopt ' ' '--includedir=.*'
var_remove_regex confopt ' ' '--infodir=.*'
var_remove_regex confopt ' ' '--sysconfdir=.*'
var_remove_regex confopt ' ' '--build=.*'
var_remove_regex confopt ' ' '--host=.*'
